OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782220721
OL,3,CPhoto released of young man who died
OL,4,Cfrom suspected stab wound in Poole
OL,6,FPolice have released an image of a
OL,7,Fteenager who died from suspected stab
OL,8,Fwound in Poole as three men are
OL,9,Fcharged in connection with his death.
OL,11,F18-year-old Kyeron Wheeler from Poole,
OL,12,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment,
OL,13,Fbut died a short time later.
OL,15,FDorset Police were called at 2.13am on
OL,16,FFriday 19 June 2026 to help a man with
OL,17,Finjuries in Longfleet Road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
