OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782220721
OL,3,CPhoto released of young man who died
OL,4,Cfrom suspected stab wound in Poole
OL,6,F"This matter will now be the subject
OL,7,Fof active court proceedings and it is
OL,8,Fvital that the criminal justice
OL,9,Fprocess is allowed to follow its
OL,10,Fcourse without prejudice. It would
OL,11,Ftherefore be inappropriate for us to
OL,12,Fcomment any further on the
OL,13,Fcircumstances surrounding this
OL,14,Fincident at this time and we would
OL,15,Furge members of the public to refrain
OL,16,Ffrom speculation and sharing of
OL,17,Finformation online or on social media.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
