PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782220721
OL,3,CPhoto released of young man who died
OL,4,Cfrom suspected stab wound in Poole
OL,6,F"Our officers will continue to provide
OL,7,Fan increased policing presence in
OL,8,Fareas impacted by this incident as we
OL,9,Ffully recognise the impact on the
OL,10,Flocal community. These officers can be
OL,11,Fapproached by anyone with questions or
OL,12,Fconcerns."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
